ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 21st day of March, 2014, the Application for Leave to File Original Process and the Petition of Habeas Corpus are DISMISSED. See Commonwealth v. Reid, 537 Pa. 167, 642 A.2d 453 (1994) (hybrid representation not permitted). The Prothonotary is directed to forward the filings to counsel of record.
